      <h3>BLUE CARBON MAPPING TOOLKIT</h3>
      <p>The tool can be used to broadly assess the impact of development on coastal marine ecosystems and the associated blue carbon stock, helping to make informed decisions relating to the future development of Abu Dhabi. For more information on using the tool, visit the help page.</p>
