      <h3>ABOUT THE DATA</h3>
      <p><img src="/assets/pages/out_on_sea.png" alt="Out on sea" id="img-out-on-sea">Baseline layers representing marine ecosystems (mangrove, salt marsh, seagrass and algal mats) around coastal Abu Dhabi were provided by the Abu Dhabi Environment Agency. They have been developed through a combination of comprehensive field based sampling, supported by Landsat and RapidEye satellite imagery analysis. Ecosystem layers have been enhanced further through input received from stakeholder consultation during the Abu Dhabi Local, National and Regional Biodiversity Assessment undertaken in 2011-13.</p>
      <p>The ecosystem layers are continually updated to reflect the ongoing dynamics of Abu Dhabi&#39;s coastal ecosystems. </p>
